Results and Conclusions¶

State-wise Deal Analysis¶

  • California and Wyoming have the highest and lowest number of deals, while the average number of deals per state is 206.

City-wise Deal Analysis¶

  • New York City has the highest number of deals of all the cities, while the average number of deals per state is 19.

Segment-wise Analysis with respect to Sales, Discount and Profit¶

  • Consumer segment contributes to the maximum sales, while Consumer segment as well as Corporate has the highest discount applicable and also, generates the maximum profits.

State-wise Analysis with respect to Sales, Discount and Profit¶

  • Wyoming has the highest sales while South Dakota has the least sales across the country.
  • Illinois Stores have the maximum discount applicable of all stores.
  • New Mexico Stores generate maximum profit while those in Colorado are undergoing highest losses.

Citywise Analysis of the Profit¶

  • Stores in Bethlehem undergo heavy losses while those at Jamestown generate huge profits.

Quantity-wise Analysis with respect to Sales, Discount and Profit¶

  • Quantity #13 has the highest sale, has maximum discount applicable and thus generates highest profit of all quantities.

Catagory-wise Analysis with respect to Sales, Discount and Profit¶

  • Technology has the highest sale and yields the most profit by a fair margin, while Furniture has highest discount applicable across the stores.

Sub-Category wise Analysis with respect to Sales, Discount and Profit¶

  • Copiers have the highest sale across the stores, while Arts has the least sale.
  • Binders have the highest discount applicable, while Labels have the least discount applicable across stores.
  • Copiers generate the maximum profit across the stores.

Regional Analysis with respect to Sales, Discount and Profit¶

  • Sales are pretty similar across the store in all four regions, but stores of Central Region have the maximum discount applicable, while the stores of West region generate the maximum profit.

Shipment Mode-wise Analysis with respect to Sales, Discount and Profit¶

  • Most sales are shipped through First-Class Shipment Mode, since it has the highest discount mode applicable and at the same time generates the maximum profit.
